data.description: Tremendous!!!4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home in Oak Park. Beautifully kept and highlights spacious open concept living with incredible smart features and custom finishes. This home is a smart home!! Motion sensor lights & faucets. Nest thermostats-doorbell camera-wifi-light switches and more! Kitchen is every chef's dream: double pantries, instant hot water, gas stove w/convection oven, beautiful tile backsplash. A custom butcher block-extended island w/seating, has pop-up wireless phone charging/electrical outlets & USB plugs. 4 spacious bedrooms upstairs. Master bath is spa quality with a custom tiled walk-in shower & dual vanities. Screened porch leads to your large, level lot with privacy fence & sprinklers. Shed & greenhouse convey. Apple, peach and pomegranate fruit bearing trees, blueberry & rosemary too. All kitchen appliances & washer/dryer convey and includes a stand alone ice machine that gives 80# of ice a day. Fire pit, roof 2019, hot water heater 2020. New Lawn Sprinkler System. Showings on Fri-Sun. only.
